name: UP CACTUS
description:
This Game is made for the Cactus Game Jam

WITH A LOT OF CACTUS

Use the mouse and left- click to attach the rope to the box

and use it to move and finish the level

This game is made in less than 2 hours

So its not that good

But feel free to comment or share this game

and if you want to support me just donate

That's all have a Nice Day
